#

Guacamole and Chips

10 min
$8.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

snackeasyparty food

Description

Fresh and creamy guacamole served with crispy tortilla chips for a perfect snack!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 3
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • tortilla chips: 1 bag
